{
  "stem": "22869.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had-- you get your-- you had your-- you got your ration of drinking, of your coffee or your tea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You got your bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we began picking up a little strength and putting on a little weight, if I can say so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, if you can picture today that-- that-- you know, when you're a skeleton, to put on a little weight under these conditions is very easy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It doesn't take a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But it was a big, big relief.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I feel today that if it wouldn't have been for this chance, that my brother and I got in this place, that things probably would've ended up with me never coming out of there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And little by little, we gained more and more strength.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it came to a point where they took us out there from there now, from the Auschwitz camp, back to Birkenau, and put us now on the real buildings to start-- perform.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "To do a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now so the beatings now came-- started to beat again, because now we had already the old supervisors and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But by now, we had already-- we were strong enough again to be able to start anew to take all this-- this-- this subhuman treatment.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it was much better than the period that I mentioned to you before with the-- with the Sonderkommando and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's-- it's in comparison today, if you take somebody and take them out from a jungle, and you put them under a controlled environment where he still has-- not good, but it's much better than the previous experiences that you had.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we kept on working on these buildings.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
